OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water plans to      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fintroduce hosepipe ban     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water has announced it is       
OL,6, planning to introduce a hosepipe ban.  
OL,8,FThe firm serves 15 million people      
OL,9,Facross parts of southern England,      
OL,10,Fincluding London.                      
OL,12,FThe company said it was planning to    
OL,13,Fannounce the temporary ban "in the     
OL,14,Fcoming weeks" but the timing is yet to 
OL,15,Fbe confirmed.                          
OL,17,FIt comes as a new heatwave nears and   
OL,18,Fthe Met Office has issued an amber     
OL,19,Fextreme heat warning for much of       
OL,20,FEngland.                               
